snippet.title: Free4All
snippet.description:
FREE4ALL is an Urban Exploring crew that is based out of Minnesota.The purpose of this channel is to document history before it is demolished. The places featured on this channel have a rich history and deserve to be documented before they are flattened by huge machinery. This channel is a historic database of abandoned and unique places. 
We DO NOT vandalize, steal, or damage property! We are simply there to take photos and document history. We do not condone urban exploration as aspects of it are very illegal. 
PLEASE do not attempt to go to any of these places as it is very unsafe and highly illegal!
NEW videos EVERY Sunday!
